s3://gaz-bucket/folder2/folder3/file1				-	folder2/folder3 is prefix\
											file1 is object name\
\
object value (content of the object)\
metadata (text key/value pairs)\
Tags (Unicode key/value pairs) - up to 10\
Version ID\
